      "content": "a break doesn't really feel like enough anymore. everything is just so heavy. like no matter how much i sleep or how much i try to pivot, the weight of just existing and having to perform every single day is exhausting. i just want the noise to stop. i want to finally be able to rest without feeling like i'm failing at something.",
