      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just feel like there's no version of the future where this doesn't happen. it's not even about the work anymore, it's just the sheer exhaustion of being alive and having to carry all this. i keep thinking about how peaceful it would be if i could just... opt out. if i didn't have to wake up and face any of this ever again. does that make sense? that just wanting everything to be still sounds better than any \"break\" could?",
